                >Continue</a>
              </div>

            </div>

            <div class="cart__block-summary">
              <h2 class="cart__block-summary-title">Your cart</h2>

              <ul class="checkout__summary-list">
                <li class="checkout__summary-item">
                  <p class="checkout__summary-text">SEEDRA Corn - Bodacious
                    Hybrid Seeds for Indoor and Outdoor Planting
                  </p>
